<h5>Strength</h5>

<p>The most important exercises for rugby players are those that use your thighs and glutes. You need these muscles to sprint, drive and to jump to your feet. Squats and burpees are essential exercises. To become a professional, you would need to exercise every muscle group regularly.</p>

